"title": "7206: community",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7206",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A group, small or large, of people. In Scripture it denotes the people of Israel, especially in pre-monarchic times and particularly during the period of the wilderness wanderings.</p>\n<h2>The community of Israel in the wilderness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:1\">EXO 16:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:1\">EXO 17:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num13:26\">NUM 13:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:22\">NUM 20:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:29\">NUM 20:29</a></p>\n<h3>Moses and Aaron communicate God's instructions to the wilderness community</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:1\">EXO 35:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:4\">EXO 35:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:20\">EXO 35:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num10:2-Num10:3\">NUM 10:2–10:3</a></p>\n<h3>Rebellion, discontent and grumbling within the wilderness community</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:2-Exod16:10\">EXO 16:2–16:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:1-Num14:2\">NUM 14:1–14:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:27\">NUM 14:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:35-Num14:36\">NUM 14:35–14:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:8-Num16:33\">NUM 16:8–16:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:41\">NUM 16:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:1-Num20:4\">NUM 20:1–20:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num27:14\">NUM 27:14</a></p>\n<h3>Responsibilities towards one another within the wilderness community</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:6\">LEV 10:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num1:53\">NUM 1:53</a></p>\n<h3>Leaders and officials, under Moses, of the wilderness community</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:22\">EXO 16:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:31\">EXO 34:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num26:9\">NUM 26:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:13\">NUM 31:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:26-Num31:27\">NUM 31:26–31:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:1-Num32:5\">NUM 32:1–32:5</a></p>\n<h3>Censuses of the wilderness community</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num1:1-Num1:3\">NUM 1:1–1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:25\">EXO 38:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num1:17-Num1:19\">NUM 1:17–1:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:34\">NUM 4:34</a></p>\n<h2>The community identity of pre-monarchic Israel</h2>\n<h3>The importance of a community identity in matters of worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev4:13-Lev4:21\">LEV 4:13–4:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:3-Exod12:19\">EXO 12:3–12:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:47-Exod12:49\">EXO 12:47–12:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:5\">LEV 16:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:32-Lev16:33\">LEV 16:32–16:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num3:6-Num3:7\">NUM 3:6–3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:9-Num8:11\">NUM 8:9–8:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:20-Num8:21\">NUM 8:20–8:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:22-Num15:26\">NUM 15:22–15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num19:9\">NUM 19:9</a></p>\n<h3>The importance of a community in legal matters</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:1-Lev20:5\">LEV 20:1–20:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:15\">NUM 15:15</a></p>\n<h2>God promised that the patriarchs' descendants would be a community of nations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:11\">GEN 35:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:3\">GEN 28:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:4\">GEN 48:4</a></p>\n<h2>The families of the priests and Levites described as a community</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:14-2Chr31:18\">2CH 31:14–31:18</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The Jews referred to as a community in NT times</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts25:24\">ACT 25:24</a></strong></p>",
